# Local-only Chinese working-notes directory — see `.git/info/exclude`.
# IMPORTANT (RELEASE.md L40-49): any personal folder with a Chinese name MUST be
# ignored via `.git/info/exclude`, NOT here. `.gitignore` is itself a tracked
# file; any CJK pattern in it is a release blocker (Phase 1, Hard Rule #1).
# The `.git/info/exclude` entry is the single source of truth — keep these
# two in sync if the folder is renamed.

